<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>403 - Access Denied | SmartBuild Ltd</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #0f111a;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #141424 0%, #0f111a 100%);
        }

        .error-card {
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(111, 66, 193, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        .display-1 {
            font-size: 8rem;
            letter-spacing: -5px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6f42c1, #a155ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .access-msg {
            color: #a155ff;
            font-weight: 500;
            background: rgba(111, 66, 193, 0.1);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px dashed rgba(161, 85, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-purple {
            background: #6f42c1;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-purple:hover {
            background: #8250df;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(111, 66, 193, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="error-container">
    <div class="text-center error-card">
        <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold">403</h1>
        
        <div style="height: 3px; width: 60px; background: #6f42c1; margin: 15px auto; border-radius: 10px;"></div>
        
        <h3 class="text-white fw-bold mb-3">ACCESS RESTRICTED</h3>
        
        <p class="access-msg mb-4">
            <i class="fas fa-user-shield me-2"></i> {{#if message}}{{message}}{{else}}You do not have the required permissions to view this resource.{{/if}}
        </p>

        <p class="text-secondary mb-4 small">
            This area of <span class="text-white fw-bold">SmartBuild ERP</span> is reserved for <strong>Administrative Staff</strong> 
            only. Please contact your supervisor if you believe this is an error.
        </p>
        
        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-purple px-4 py-2">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left me-2"></i> RETURN TO SAFETY
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>